query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk t k) */ select min(t.title) AS movie_title
from title AS t
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year < 2013
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword like '%sequel%'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Norway',
'Germany',
'Denmark',
'Swedish',
'Denish',
'Norwegian',
'German');
